Task: 03
Title: Application passthrough use case
Phase: 1
Route: full
Slice: Passthrough Chat Completion (OpenAI)
Dependencies: 01, 02
Scope: Define the FusionService inbound port (runFusion returns AsyncIterable<FusionStreamEvent>) and implement a passthrough RunFusionUseCase that calls ChatModelPort.complete() against the synthesizer model and yields a single content_delta + done stream event. The use case constructor accepts ChatModelPort, ConfigPort, LoggerPort, and ClockPort via dependency injection. This task establishes the application layer with zero infrastructure imports.
Acceptance Criteria: AC-4
NFRs: NFR-1
Gate Criteria: Phase 1 Gate 2 (zero SDK/framework imports in application)
Files:
  - src/application/ports/fusion-service.ts (CREATE) — FusionService interface: runFusion(request: FusionRequest): AsyncIterable<FusionStreamEvent>
  - src/application/usecases/run-fusion-use-case.ts (CREATE) — RunFusionUseCase class implementing FusionService; passthrough mode: calls ChatModelPort.complete() with synthesizer model, wraps response as FusionStreamEvent
